WKP Karst Window Analysis

Seth Bassett, GISP
September 25, 2015

Query

sql = "
SELECT * FROM analysis.insitu_salt_hourly 
  WHERE 
    date_time >= \'2009-01-01 00:00:00 UTC\' 
      AND 
    date_time < \'2012-12-31 00:00:00 UTC\' AND elev_ft > 0 
      AND 
    site_name != \'St. Marks River Rise (Surface)\' 
  ORDER BY 
    date_time;"

insitu <- dbGetQuery(db, sql)

  • Select appropriate time frame (2009-2012)
  • Exclude elevation values < 0
  • Exclude St. Marks River Rise
  • Order results by date_time column
